\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces  \textsc  {TwoRoom} closed-loop compression frontier. Success rates are measured over \(n=64\) episodes with seed \(0\). The teacher achieves \(76.56\%\) success. Activation-aware SVD preserves near-teacher performance across most compression levels, while operator-aware distillation is not consistently better than direct low-rank compression. }}{16}{figure.caption.6}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{fig:tworoom-frontier}{{1}{16}{\textsc {TwoRoom} closed-loop compression frontier. Success rates are measured over \(n=64\) episodes with seed \(0\). The teacher achieves \(76.56\%\) success. Activation-aware SVD preserves near-teacher performance across most compression levels, while operator-aware distillation is not consistently better than direct low-rank compression}{figure.caption.6}{}}
